  "description": {
   "en": "The reign of the 13th emperor of the glittering country. A lonely girl, Shoko, fights to protect her only sister. Under the supervision of Ao, a government official who noticed her ability, she was assigned to a certain job while dressed in black. Then she meets the emperor, Shu Xiao...!　\n\nTwo men and a girl interweave in this dramatic Chinese spectacular romance!\n\n---\nNote: Originally a oneshot series, starting with \"Amakakeru Ookami\" parts 1-2 in Flowers 2/2021 issue and 3/2021 issue on December 28, 2020, and January 28, 2021, respectively. Magazine serialization started in Flowers 5/2022 issue on March 28, 2022. The oneshots are included in the volume 1 release."
